data.description: Come see this gem in excellent condition located in the Highly Desired Cinco Ranch community in Katy TX!   Cinco Ranch features world-class amenities, highly rated schools, & easy freeway access! This home is nestled in a peaceful forest setting of well-distanced trees in an expansive yard. The classic patio & the attractive brick walls draw immediate attention to this home. Light and bright kitchen with stainless appliances and breakfast room. The stunning kitchen has updated quartz counter tops. The seller is open to contributing towards a professional paint update, ensuring the home meets the buyer's vision. This presents a wonderful opportunity for the new owner to customize the interior to their liking, creating a space that truly feels like home.
